Package: watchguard
Version: 1.0.2
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Solaris17 <solaris17@outlook.com>
Depends: systemd
Description: Watchguard host health monitor
 Watchguard monitors host health using systemd, journald, SSH, network,
 DNS, and OOM checks with configurable remediation actions, persistent
 state, and journald logging.
